message.entry: The file ''{0}'' and dataset ''{1}'' do not exist. See H5CREATE.

The amount of data to be written does not match the size of the HDF5 dataset.
The size of the data to be written does not match up with the size of the HDF5 dataset.
The amount of data to be written does not match up with the COUNT argument.

START and COUNT (and optionally STRIDE) must be specified when writing to a dataset with at least one unlimited dimension.
